#ad I’m very excited to share @narwalrobot with you. Narwal is the World’s 1st self-cleaning robot mop and vacuum. It’s really the best #cleaninghack this mama has found yet! You can remotely control the robot with the App from anywhere. Click the link in my bio to pre-order now with $1 to save $180 on June 1. The #narwalt10 is so intelligent that it separates paths for sweeping and mopping. It’s really amazing because it automatically detects when the mop heads are dirty too. The #robot will return to the station for cleaning and drying. Once clean the robot restarts the task. Narwal is absolutely terrific at maneuvering from floor to carpet, under, and between furniture. I’m so impressed at how well this #robotvacuum sweeps and mops my home. Narwal allows me more free time to spend with the family. You should definitely check it out by clicking the link in my bio. #robotmop

https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket (Ad) Get your kiddos outside and active with the @theoriginalstomprocket from @target. This makes a fantastic holiday gift for ages 5 and up. We received the Stomp Rocket Stunt Planes High Flying Planes with Launch Pad 3pk.  https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket 🚀
Dominic and Scotty are having a blast stomping, jumping, and running to launch the rockets.  Active play is so important for kids. Having them participate in #unpluggedplay is beneficial for their overall development. This toy combines working on #stemlearning and #grossmotorskills all while having a great time! 🚀
I love that the Stomp Rocket 🚀 has kiddos using their brain and muscle power. The boys are having a lot of fun trying to launch the rocket at different angles, into a box, and the basketball hoop. It’s great watching the boys thinking, discussing, and trying new ideas with this toy. As a mom and early childhood educator this is the type of toy I get excited about! 🚀

(Ad) You know how much we love crafting, playing, and doing activities with Wikki Stix @mywikkistix. We are super excited to introduce you to FIDGIT STIX which is a new twist on the original #wikkistix! A colorful way to get some hands on #fidget therapy. Each set comes with 36 non toxic vibrant colors in a reusable poly bag for storage. These are awesome for traveling, zoom meetings, down time, errands, play dates, and creative fun at home. 

We really enjoy sensory play, fidget toys, and tactile experiences. Fidgit Stix are all of this in one! They are soft, pliable, and quiet. You can easily twist, bend, and shape them over and over. Fidgit Stix are great for helping to soothe, calm, and relax. Fidget toys are beneficial for kiddos, teens, and adults. They help with learning, reducing anxiety and stress, enhancing dexterity, improving coordination, strengthening fine motor skills, and assisting in the development of small hand muscles. Check the new Fidgit Stix out here https://www.wikkistix.com/product/fidget-stix/ or by clicking the link in my bio @greeneclecticmama.
